---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
/* Asegúrate de poner la ruta correcta de tu logo aquí */
---

<footer class="bg-black border-t border-white/10 pt-12 pb-4">
  <div class="max-w-[1600px] mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-10">
      <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 flex flex-col items-start gap-4">
        <div class="h-24">
          <Image
            width={327}
            height={311}
            src="/assets/winay.webp"
            alt="Wiñay Agency"
            loading="lazy"
            class="h-full object-contain"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mt-2">
          Ayudamos a marcas a escalar sus resultados a través de estrategias
          digitales de alto impacto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-2">
          Contacto
        </h3>

        <a
          href="tel:51969114948"
          class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-[#e6007e] transition-colors group"
        >
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#e6007e]/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm">+51 969 114 948</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="mailto:winaycomercial@gmail.com"
          class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-[#e6007e] transition-colors group"
        >
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#e6007e]/20 transition-colors"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
              ></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm">winaycomercial@gmail.com</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-2">
          Ubicación
        </h3>
        <a
          href="https://goo.gl/maps/..."
          target="_blank"
          class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300 hover:text-[#e6007e] transition-colors group"
        >
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-[#e6007e]/20 transition-colors shrink-0"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-4 h-4"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"
              ></path><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg
            >
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm leading-snug"
            >Albaricoques 231<br />La Molina, Lima - Perú</span
          >
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h3 class="text-white font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mb-2">
          Datos Fiscales
        </h3>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-[#e6007e] font-bold">RUC:</span> 20614057093
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-[#e6007e] font-bold">Razón social:</span> MK AGENCY SAC
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div
      class="border-t border-white/20 pt-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-4"
    >
      <p class="text-gray-200 text-xs">
        © 2026  Wiñay Agency. Todos los derechos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
